IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: On February 20, 2023, TFC Mulhearn of the Maryland State Police Centreville Barrack arrested Rodney Drake Anderson for felony CDS violations and firearms related charges. Anderson was found to be in possession of a black IPhone 11, serial# FFWJY573N72J and a Blue android cellphone model: DE2118 serial# CC535FLE. CPL Mozet from the Maryland State Police Firearms Enforcement Unit responded to the Centreville Barrack and took possession of the cellphones. CPL Mozet authored a search and seizure warrant for the above mentioned cellphones which was signed by the Honorable Judge Marsh of the District Court for Wicomico, Maryland. CPL Mozet conducted a hand search of the cellphones. I took possession of the cellphones and utilized a Cellebrite Universal Forensic Extraction Device (UFED) and downloaded the phones. I was not able to locate any items of eventiary value on the IPhone.
